Hi everybody,

I'm just getting familiar with Name Servers and I have the following questions.
Can anyone answer them for me ?

- Is it possible to make sure a server query is directly answered by a name
  server which is not within your domain but of which you do know the
  addresses ?
  This because we want to use private TCP-IP lines without first asking our
  parent etc. etc. Otherwise our parent would ask his parent etc and much
  time can be won by asking directly to the known-server.

- Is it possible keep zone-information on other machines then the host 
  on which the Name Servers resites ? 

Please mail answers (if you have any) to a20@np1.hep.nl

Thanx.

Marten Terpstra Nikhef-H Amsterdam Holland.
